OL,5, Senior lieutenant Pavel Kuzin took his 
OL,6, position at the machine gun - the only 
OL,7, soldier still able to fight. Everyone  
OL,8, else in his troop lay dead or injured. 
OL,10,FSuffering from shell-shock and with one
OL,11,Farm bandaged, the 37-year-old fired at 
OL,12,Fthe waves of Russian soldiers trying to
OL,13,Fstorm his position. They didn't even   
OL,14,Ftry to take cover, but simply walked   
OL,15,Ftowards him across the open field.     
